{% if tofu_context == 'org' %}
| Layer | File | Purpose |
|-------|------|---------|
| Providers | `versions.tf` | Required provider versions and sources |
| State | `backend.tf` | Remote state backend configuration |
| Variables | `variables.tf` | Input variables — required, optional, sensitive, validated |
| Resources | `main.tf` | Provider blocks and resource definitions |
| Outputs | `outputs.tf` | Values consumed by application repos via remote state |
{% else %}
| Step | Tool | Purpose |
|------|------|---------|
| 1. Source env | `source .env` | Load secrets into environment |
| 2. Init | `tofu init` | Install providers and backend |
| 3. Plan | `tofu plan` | Preview changes |
| 4. Apply | `tofu apply` | Deploy infrastructure |
{% endif %}
